headline: RSG Q3 Deep Dive: Margin Expansion Amid Flat Volumes and Environmental Headwinds
summary: Waste management company Republic Services (NYSE:RSG) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025 as sales rose 3.3% year on year to $4.21 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.90 per share was 6.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
